summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lots 16 to 19, inclusive, Block 3, Furth's Addition, Lots 13 to 24, inclusive, Block B, Phinney's Addition, and Lots 13 to 24, inclusive, Block 4, Sarah B.
